title: The Drinky Crow Show S1 (DrinkyCrow)
description:
Based on the weekly comic-strip "Maakies", an alcoholic crow named Drinky Crow and a drunken Irish monkey named Uncle Gabby, set sail in an eighteenth century nautical setting.

Drinky Crow & Uncle Gabby are crew members in Captain Maak's ship. They're currently in war with the French (Alligators), but usually they slack off and drink in the local town harbor.
